org.apache.james.imap.api.message.response

Interface StatusResponseFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstactStatusResponseFactory, UnpooledStatusResponseFactory

    public interface StatusResponseFactory
    Constructs StatusResponse instances. This interface enforces RFC2060 rules.
